1. *Supruga* ga je veoma razočarala (His wife disappointed him very much).
2. On se nadao da će njegova *supruga* biti srećnija (He was hoping his wife would be happier).
3. On je došao kući sa svojom *suprugom* (He came home with his wife).
4. Oni su napravili plan da njegova *supruga* bude uključena (They made a plan to include his wife).
5. Njegova *supruga* je bila vrlo zauzeta (His wife was very busy).